[It is unclear what role the hotel worker (?food handler) has had in the outbreak. If this was the case, one might have seen a secondary cluster since the incubation period is 2-3 weeks generally. The story of Typhoid Mary, Mary Mallon, can be found at http://history1900s.about.com/od/1900s/a/typhoidmary.htm. - Mod.LL]

[Harare can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Zimbabwe at http://healthmap.org/r/1r1O. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
